data.actual_result: Quick switcher shows the page you were on, minus the servers at the top, before showing search results
data.expected_result: Search results pop up right after you type a letter
data.short_description: Searching in the Quick Switcher while having suggested channels will show the suggested channels for a second before showing search results
data.steps_to_repro: - Open the quick switcher in a server you have multiple unread channels - Type any letter into the quick switcher - Observe the results that pop up after typing
